Spain













Edmond de Rothschild (Europe), S.E. (formerly Banque Privée Edmond de Rothschild Europe, S.E.)
 


overview

Financials
Deposit Guarantee
Bank Identifiers
Locations



  


















Edmond de Rothschild is a family-owned financial group, 
specialising in private banking and asset management. Edmond de Rothschild group also 
provides corporate finance, private equity and fund administration solutions. Edmond de Rothschild (Europe), S.E. operates as a branch of Edmond de Rothschild (Europe) (Luxembourg). In 2016 total assets of Edmond de Rothschild (Europe), S.E.  were 39,06 mln EUR.   Edmond de Rothschild (Europe), S.E. participates in deposit guarantee scheme of Luxembourg. 
This scheme covers accounts up to 100 000 EUR per bank per depositor.  Edmond de Rothschild (Europe), S.E. is located in Madrid.




AddressPs de la Castellana, 55, 28046, Madrid, Spain 

HeadquartersEdmond de Rothschild (Europe) (Luxembourg)Bank CategoryBranches of foreign banks  
 


Total Assets (2016)39.06 mln EUR  (+38.55%)  

Deposit Guarantee100 000 EUR  
 


