Rothschild family

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia
  (Redirected from Rothschild Family)

					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

"House of Rothschild" redirects here. For the film, see The House of Rothschild. For other uses, see Rothschild (disambiguation).

Rothschild


Arms granted to the Barons Rothschild by Emperor Francis I of Austria



Ethnicity
Jewish


Current region
Western Europe; above all the United Kingdom, France and Germany[1]


